=== CAFETERIA PLASMOID ===

== BUILD REQUIREMENTS ==
Packages for SUSE:
* libplasma1
* kdebase4-workspace-devel

== BUILDING ==
$ mkdir build
$ cd build
$ cmake -DPLUGIN_INSTALL_DIR=/usr/lib64/kde4/ -DSERVICES_INSTALL_DIR=/usr/share/kde4/services/ ..
$ make
$ sudo make install
$ sudo kbuildsycoca4

to test it, you can run:
$ plasmoidviewer cafeteria

to use it, log out and in again and you should be able to see the plasmoid in
the list of available plasmoids.
